name: Rina Ellis
description:
Rina Ellis (born April 15, 1993), also known as Little Miss Rina, was born in Seoul, South Korea. Making her adult entertainment debut in 2016 around the age of 23, she quickly found work for studios and websites including Brazzers, Digital Playground, Babes.com, and Reality Kings.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey nice people! This is my textual inversion of Rina Ellis. I used 60 public images of her, with a 5200 steps training process. She's one of my favorites ever... Hope you'll like it! To use it in your works:

  • like Eva Elfie's textual inversion, this one is also particularly horny 😂 check the examples for some inspiration about the prompt;

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add rinellis93 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20, and CFG around 7 seems to work well. No face restore and great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision. Check the gallery for some inspiration!
